<h4 id="corner-sizing-shorthand">
Sizing All Corners At Once:
The 'border-radius' shorthand</h4>

	<pre class="propdef shorthand">
		Name: border-radius
		Value: <<length-percentage [0,&infin;]>>{1,4} [ / <<length-percentage [0,&infin;]>>{1,4} ]?
